### Get all resources
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/external/resources

### Get resource by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/external/resources/1

### Get resources by user ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/external/resources/search?userId=1

### Create new resource
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/external/resources
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "message": "This is a test message"
}

### Update resource
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/external/resources/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe Updated",
  "email": "john.updated@example.com",
  "message": "This is an updated message"
}

### Partial update resource
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/external/resources/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Partially Updated"
}

### Delete resource
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/external/resources/1

### Get resource with custom headers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/external/resources/1/with-headers
X-Custom-Header: CustomValue
X-Another-Header: AnotherValue

### Submit form data
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/external/resources/form
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=John&email=john@example.com&message=Form data test

### Get resource with status handling
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/external/resources/1/with-status-handling

### Get resource with full response
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/external/resources/1/full-response